<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="<%= lang %>">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Furry Tails Photography - Pet Photographer</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
  <!-- Icons from Lucide (https://lucide.dev) - ISC License -->
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('navbar') %>

  <main>
    <section class="hero-grid">
      <div class="container-fluid">
        <div class="hero-cards">
          <!-- Left Column -->
          <div class="hero-column hero-column-left">
            <!-- Card 1: Teal -->
            <div class="hero-card card-teal">
              <div class="card-text-container">
                <h2><span>Studio pet portraits.</span><span>Brag-worthy. Timeless.</span></h2>
                <p>Treat your pet to a professional studio session filled with play, treats and perfect results that highlight their unique character.</p>
                <div class="card-buttons">
                  <a href="/<%= lang %>/contact" class="card-btn">BOOK A SESSION →</a>
                  <a href="/<%= lang %>/gallery" class="card-btn">VIEW GALLERY →</a>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="card-image">
                <picture>
                  <source media="(max-width: 480px)" srcset="/gallery/hero1a.jpg">
                  <img src="/gallery/Hero2.jpg" alt="Pet portrait" class="pet-img">
                </picture>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Card 3: Light Blue -->
            <div class="hero-card card-lightblue">
              <div class="card-text-container">
                <h2>Relaxed sessions, at your pet's pace.</h2>
                <p>Whether your dog is energetic or a bit unsure, the photo session adapts to them.</p>
                <a href="/<%= lang %>/how-it-works" class="card-btn">HOW IT WORKS →</a>
              </div>
              <div class="card-image">
                <img src="/gallery/Hero4.jpg" alt="Pet portrait" class="pet-img">
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Right Column -->
          <div class="hero-column hero-column-right">
            <!-- Card 2: Pink -->
            <div class="hero-card card-pink">
              <div class="card-text-container">
                <h2><span>Clean setup. Perfect light.</span><span>No distractions.</span></h2>
                <p>Carefully chosen backdrops, soft direction, and attention to detail — so the focus stays where it should be.</p>
                <a href="/<%= lang %>/prices" class="card-btn">PRICES →</a>
              </div>
              <div class="card-image">
                <img src="/gallery/Hero1.jpg" alt="Pet portrait" class="pet-img">
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Card 4: Brown -->
            <div class="hero-card card-brown">
              <div class="card-text-container">
                <h2>READY WHEN YOU ARE</h2>
                <p>Whether you want to book or just have a few questions, feel free to get in touch.</p>
                <a href="/<%= lang %>/contact" class="card-btn">CONTACT →</a>
              </div>
              <div class="card-image">
                <img src="/gallery/Hero3.jpg" alt="Pet portrait" class="pet-img">
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="about-section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="about-wrapper">
          <div class="about-text">
            <h3>HI, I'M ANNA.</h3>
            <h2>A PET PHOTOGRAPHER BASED IN BERLIN</h2>
            <p>I create vibrant, authentic portraits for pets and people who love them. Most of the time, the best photos happen in between moments. That's what I look for during a session.</p>
            <a href="/<%= lang %>/about" class="btn-link">MORE ABOUT ME →</a>
          </div>

          <div class="about-features">
            <div class="feature">
              <div class="feature-icon">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-camera"><path d="M13.997 4a2 2 0 0 1 1.76 1.05l.486.9A2 2 0 0 0 18.003 7H20a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v9a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H4a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V9a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h1.997a2 2 0 0 0 1.759-1.048l.489-.904A2 2 0 0 1 10.004 4z"/><circle cx="12" cy="13" r="3"/></svg>
              </div>
              <h4>NATURAL & AUTHENTIC</h4>
              <p>No stiff poses</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
              <div class="feature-icon">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-heart"><path d="M2 9.5a5.5 5.5 0 0 1 9.591-3.676.56.56 0 0 0 .818 0A5.49 5.49 0 0 1 22 9.5c0 2.29-1.5 4-3 5.5l-5.492 5.313a2 2 0 0 1-3 .019L5 15c-1.5-1.5-3-3.2-3-5.5"/></svg>
              </div>
              <h4>EXPERIENCE MATTERS</h4>
              <p>A relaxed, joyful session</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
              <div class="feature-icon">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-star"><path d="M11.525 2.295a.53.53 0 0 1 .95 0l2.31 4.679a2.123 2.123 0 0 0 1.595 1.16l5.166.756a.53.53 0 0 1 .294.904l-3.736 3.638a2.123 2.123 0 0 0-.611 1.878l.882 5.14a.53.53 0 0 1-.771.56l-4.618-2.428a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-1.973 0L6.396 21.01a.53.53 0 0 1-.77-.56l.881-5.139a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-.611-1.879L2.16 9.795a.53.53 0 0 1 .294-.906l5.165-.755a2.122 2.122 0 0 0 1.597-1.16z"/></svg>
              </div>
              <h4>ART YOU'LL LOVE</h4>
              <p>Beautiful, timeless portraits</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <%- include('footer') %>
</body>
</html>
